x4freetext: Gold was adopted for
the standard. All values of measured resonance
integrals have been corrected to correspond to the
1513 barn value for gold and, somewhat arbitrarily,
to the 45 barn addition for 1/v contribution which
correctly should depend on whether a beam flux or an
isotropic flux was used and exactly how thick the
cadmium shield was.
